rows.label: qst104703_msg001
rows.name:
At this time of year, Liberalitas is between
Superbia and Gula, so maybe they're just
stopping for a rest as a relay point.

rows.label: qst104703_msg0002
rows.name:
You're the ones who were speaking
with Enju before we set sail.

rows.label: qst104703_msg0003
rows.name:
Did you happen to see another Divine
Beast ship on your way here?

rows.label: qst104703_msg0004
rows.name:
I see... The moment we arrived in
Liberalitas, the weather turned bad.

rows.label: qst104703_msg0005
rows.name:
We were unlucky enough to
be attacked by Cloud Sea
life and got separated.

rows.label: qst104703_msg0006
rows.name:
I want to go search... but
Enju is on the other ship,
and I can't fight...

rows.label: qst104703_msg0007
rows.name: Will you really? That's a huge help!

rows.label: qst104703_msg0008
rows.name:
The people of Iyasaki Village said
there don't seem to be any Imperial
ships on this side of the Cloud Ridge.

rows.label: qst104703_msg0009
rows.name:
I think Enju is fine, but
I wonder if the people on
the ship are okay...

rows.label: qst104703_msg0101
rows.name:
There are many strong people
in the world who can fight
without being Drivers.

rows.label: qst104703_msg0102
rows.name:
As for me, without Enju, I can't
even think of fighting...

rows.label: qst104703_msg0201
rows.name:
You found them!? Enju, too...
is safe! Thank goodness...

rows.label: qst104703_msg0202
rows.name:
It was buried in the Cloud
Sea and couldn't move...

rows.label: qst104703_msg0203
rows.name: Could you tell me its exact location?

rows.label: qst104703_msg0205
rows.name:
If we tow it with this ship, we
should be able to make it to Gula.

rows.label: qst104703_msg0206
rows.name:
The people at Yeshiva
Harbor offered to help,
so the rest should be fine.
